sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant C1 as Cliente A
    participant C2 as Cliente B
    participant FE as Angular Frontend
    participant API as ASP.NET Core API
    participant RS as ReservationService
    participant Repo as ReservationRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    C1->>FE: Selecciona slot disponible
    C2->>FE: Selecciona el mismo slot disponible

    par Requests concurrentes
        C1->>API: POST /api/public/reservations
        API->>RS: Create reservation A
        RS->>Repo: ExistsOverlappingAsync(space, start, end)
        Repo->>DB: Buscar reserva solapada
        DB-->>Repo: No existe
        RS->>DB: Insert reservation A
        DB-->>RS: Insert OK
        RS-->>API: Reserva creada
        API-->>C1: 201 Created
    and
        C2->>API: POST /api/public/reservations
        API->>RS: Create reservation B
        RS->>Repo: ExistsOverlappingAsync(space, start, end)
        Repo->>DB: Buscar reserva solapada
        DB-->>Repo: Puede no verla por concurrencia
        RS->>DB: Insert reservation B
        DB-->>RS: Restricción de solapamiento falla
        RS-->>API: ReservationConflictException
        API-->>C2: 409 Conflict
    end

    Note over DB: PostgreSQL es la garantía final contra overbooking.
